To answer the question as to why this was rated 4 forks by both reviewers but only 50% would make it again: The ratings (1-4 forks) and whether or not you would make the recipe again are not dependent on one another. Someone can rate a recipe as being great- 4 forks, yet are not likely to make it a second time for whatever reason (too time consuming, difficult to locate ingredients, etc.) one of the reviewers must have answered "no" to making the dish again.

